%h3 Task A

%h4 Ruby On Rails FizzBuzz application

%p Standard FizzBuzz rules, divisible by 3 is Fizz, divisible by 5 is Buzz
%ul
  %li Should display values from 1 to 100 on the homepage
  %li Should allow viewing values up to 100,000,000,000
  %li Should have pagination (not from libraries)
  %li Should allow changing of the page size
  %li User should be able to mark certain numbers as their favourites, these should indicate that they are favourites on the UI and be persisted
  %li Should provide a JSON API with all the above-mentioned functionality

